Minimize[L, {b0, b1}] // Simplify // N\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"1b758df0-11a5-4ff2-b413-a445ff132286"],

Cell["\<\
data = {{1, 2, 3}, {1, 3, 6}, {2, 5, 3}, {3, 7, 6}};
X = DesignMatrix[data, {X1, X2}, {X1, X2}];
y = data[[All, -1]];
Inverse[Transpose[X] . X] . Transpose[X] . y\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"34a2a6d9-8ece-4023-bc1f-dc7542fc6a4b"],

Cell["PseudoInverse[X] . y", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"765c8a69-3bac-4347-9633-4a42ace9cd3b"],

Cell["\<\
b = {b0, b1, b2};
L = (y - X . b) . (y - X . b);
Reduce[{D[L, {b}] == {0, 0, 0}}]\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"b2f0db92-5a9d-42d1-8a70-07211fa91f89"],

Cell["\<\
D[L, {b}] == -2 Transpose[X] . y + 2 Transpose[X] . X . b // Simplify\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"5711ed5d-77c9-4217-bf0d-89c76958e6fc"],

Cell["\<\
data = {{1, 2, 3}, {1, 3, 6}, {2, 5, 3}, {3, 7, 6}};
